{{地區用詞|cn=白汁|tw=白醬|hk=cn|as=稱為|start={{lang-fr|'''Sauce béchamel'''}}；{{IPA-fr|be.ʃa'mɛl|lang}}；{{IPAc-en|b|ɛ|ʃ|ə|ˈ|m|ɛ|l}}或{{IPAc-en|b|eɪ|ʃ|ə|ˈ|m|ɛ|l}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/bechamel|title=Béchamel definition|work=Merriam-Webster|access-date=2013-03-13|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630013420/https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/bechamel|dead-url=no}}</ref>}}，或音譯作'''貝夏媚醬'''<ref name=watermouth>{{cite web |url=http://watermouth.wordpress.com/category/five-mother-sauces%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E6%AF%8D%E9%86%AC/ |title=「Five Mother Sauces五大法式母醬」分類文章彙整 |publisher=[http://watermouth.wordpress.com/ 香草心] |date=2011-02-12 |access-date=2013-03-12 |language=zh-hant |archive-date=2014-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024021342/http://watermouth.wordpress.com/category/five-mother-sauces%E4%BA%94%E5%A4%A7%E6%B3%95%E5%BC%8F%E6%AF%8D%E9%86%AC/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是一種基本[[醬汁|醬汁]]。

白汁是将[[黄油|奶油]]和[[麵粉|麵粉]]煮成的[[奶油炒麵糊|奶油炒麵糊]]放入[[牛奶|牛奶]]中煮制成的。白汁常用於製作其他醬汁，如：[[乾酪白汁|乾酪白汁]]（Mornay sauce，[[芝士|芝士]]加上白汁）等，是[[法國菜|法國菜]]的五大[[母醬|母醬]]之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://whatscookingamerica.net/History/SauceHistory.htm |last=Stradley |first=Linda |work=What's Cooking America |title=Sauces - History of Sauces |access-date=2012-06-29 |language=en |archive-date=2008-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080116161818/http://whatscookingamerica.net/History/SauceHistory.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也常見於[[意大利美食|意大利美食]]的許多食譜，如[[千層麵|千層麵]]等。相傳這種醬是由法國的[[路易·德·貝夏媚|路易·德·貝夏媚]]所創。

